Que Link: https://xingxingpark.com/Leetcode-1084-Sales-Analysis-III/(This link has wrong result)

Ans: 

select p.product_id, p.product_name from Product p left join Sales s on p.product_id=s.product_id where s.sale_date between '2019-01-01' and '2019-03-31'
 
Note:  when there is no primary key, use Group by and use aggregate functions in Having instead of using in Where

